data.title: Camillo Rüdiger von Starhemberg (1804
data.meta_description: Camillo Rüdiger, 4.Fürst von Starhemberg, was the son of Karl Gundakar, Graf von Starhemberg, and his wife, Gräfin Maria von Colloredo.  He was married in 1834 to Guidobaldine Steinmetz (d. 1835), with whom he had issue.  Following her death, he was married at Schwertberg on August 28, 1838 to Gräfin Marie Leopoldine...
